<plot>"Young Gentlemen" chronicles a day in the life of Troy, an aimless sex crazed teenager who spends all his time partying, hanging out, and getting laid all the while ignoring his parent's wishes to focus on school and not hang out with his friends and girlfriend. One night out with his friends they meet up with some girls. His friends have sexual intercourse with one of the girls. Finding her offer suspect, Troy opts not have intercourse with her. Later that night, they learn from some friends looking for this girl that she is HIV positive. His friends take drastic action while Troy tries to stop them. He fails to and leaves the scene. Changed by these events, he breaks up with his girlfriend and begins to understand his parents concern and the error of his ways.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?666996</url></doc>
